OL,3,COlympic star fears Chinese swimmers'
OL,4,Cfailed drugs tests risk 'tarnishing'
OL,5,Csport
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Sports Producer Joe
OL,8,FWardropper
OL,10,FBritain's Olympic Matt Richards says
OL,11,Fthe news that 23 Chinese athletes who
OL,12,Ftested positive for a banned substance
OL,13,Fwere allowed to compete in the 2021
OL,14,FTokyo Olympics risks undermining his
OL,15,Fsport's reputation, less than 100 days
OL,16,Fahead of the Paris Games.
