OL,3,COlympic star fears Chinese swimmers'
OL,4,Cfailed drugs tests risk 'tarnishing'
OL,5,Csport
OL,7,F"I've had seven drugs' tests in 2024,
OL,8,Fand we're not even in May yet... I can
OL,9,Fstand here categorically and say I'm
OL,10,Fclean in every way there is and to
OL,11,Fknow you have to race against people
OL,12,Fwho maybe aren't taking this as
OL,13,Fseriously is really frustrating," he
OL,14,Ftold ITV News.
OL,16,FThe Chinese swimmers' positive tests
OL,17,Femerged after a joint investigation by
OL,18,FThe New York Times and the German
OL,19,Fbroadcaster ARD.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/7
