OL,3,COlympic star fears Chinese swimmers'
OL,4,Cfailed drugs tests risk 'tarnishing'
OL,5,Csport
OL,7,F"As soon as public opinion about how
OL,8,Fclean a sport is starts to go
OL,9,Fdownhill," Mr Richards told ITV News.
OL,10,F"It's a slippery slope, and it's very
OL,11,Fquick that the whole sport is
OL,12,Ftarnished with the same brush.
OL,14,F"I know some of the guys on the
OL,15,FChinese team, I'm friends with some of
OL,16,Fthose guys and I get on with them, I
OL,17,Fdon't know whether or not they are
OL,18,Fclean, I don't know whether they are
OL,19,Fdoping, for all I know, they might not
OL,20,Fknow, even if they were doping, it's a
OL,21,Freally tough one," Mr Richards said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
