OL,3,COlympic star fears Chinese swimmers'
OL,4,Cfailed drugs tests risk 'tarnishing'
OL,5,Csport
OL,7,F"I was there, I was in the apartment
OL,8,Fbuilding with the guys like Duncan
OL,9,FScott who was beaten by one of the
OL,10,Fathletes named in that list and could
OL,11,Fbe stood here as an Olympic champion
OL,12,Findividually," he added.
OL,14,FDuncan Scott - his teammate in the
OL,15,Fgold medal winning 4x200m freestyle
OL,16,Frelay team in Tokyo - lost out in the
OL,17,F200m men's medley to Wang Shun, one of
OL,18,Fthe Chinese swimmers who tested
OL,19,Fpositive for the banned drug.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
