OL,5,Csport
OL,7,FOn Saturday, Mr Richards' Olympic
OL,8,Fteammate James Guy, wrote on X: "Wow.
OL,9,FBan them all and never compete again."
OL,11,F"I don't know that banning them all is
OL,12,Fthe right option," Mr Richards told
OL,13,FITV News. "Because there will be guys
OL,14,Fin there who are clean...It does make
OL,15,Fyou question things when you see 23
OL,16,Fathletes from the same country, at the
OL,17,Fsame camp, all test positive for the
OL,18,Fsame drug."
